subject: College Athletics
NCAA Lacrosse Championships
Lacrosse
lead_paragraph: Trailing 12-5 in the second half, the Orange staged a miraculous comeback, outscoring No. 1 Florida by 8-1 in the final 12 minutes of regulation in an N.C.A.A. women’s lacrosse semifinal.
